rt to curb the violence. But killings of Hindus and moderate Sikhs escalated. At least 2,400 were killed by Sikh militants last year, more than double the number killed in 1987. More than 340 people have died this year. On Friday, <PERSON> Gandhi </PERSON> announced a peace initiative. In addition to the release of political detainees, <PERSON> Gandhi </PERSON> said foreigners now can travel to <LOCATION> Punjab </LOCATION> without special government permission. He also said elections will be held, starting May, for village committees to supervise development work and law and order.
