o so exists. The <PERSON> Farabundo </PERSON> <PERSON> Marti </PERSON> on Saturday said direct talks with the government on their proposal must be held Tuesday and Wednesday in <LOCATION> San </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Salvador </LOCATION>, the capital. It repeated its accusation that the government was procrastinating. The civil war has killed an estimated 70,000 people, most of them civilians.
